---
title: Bangladeshi Chicken Curry with Cauliflower,  Zucchini and Mint Chutney
description: This fresh, fragrant curry gets it’s flavour from a delicious Bangladeshi curry powder. A mild yet tasty base of ginger, garlic, mild chili powder and spices is revived with fresh lime and creamy crema, all on a bed of pillowy rice. Divine!
